ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Recommended for fellow students in pre-modern Chinese literature
Go and take it! Six Dynasties witnessed more cool people.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It covers a time period of Chinese poetry, which is important but usually overlooked in graduate level courses

The seminar extended my interest and knowledge about a unique period in Chinese history. The writings and biographies about figures with strong personality provide insight into some traditions of Chinese intellectuals.
